<h2> Timepiece </h2>
<p class="giDescription">
Let Us Go Then, You And I (In The Room The Women Come And Go),... For T.S. Elliot, who's poem, The Lovesong of J. Alfred Prufrock is embedded in this painting, plus a note on John Keats and Jane Campion.
</p>
<div class="block-core-ItemInfo giInfo">
<div class="date summary">
Date: 02/12/2004
</div>
</div>
</div>
