<h3>
A Thing Of Beauty---On Jane Campion's Film Bright Star, John Keats, Fanny Braune, and the Beauty of  Watching Wet Paint Dry
</h3>
<span class="showFull">
| <a id="comment-more-toggle-5592-571565668"
